    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Deduplicate Event\n\n**Purpose:** Prevents duplicate event processing by checking hash-based signatures against Supabase.\n\n**Process:**\n1. Compute SHA-256 hash from source + dedup_key\n2. Query Supabase events table for existing hash\n3. If duplicate found → return existing event ID\n4. If new → insert event record with \"processing\" status → return new event ID\n\n**Input Required:**\n- `source` (enum: gmail, drive, webhook, form)\n- `dedup_key` (unique identifier for the event)\n- `event_type` (type of event being processed)\n\n**Output:**\n- `isDuplicate` (boolean)\n- `existing_event_id` OR `event_id`",
        "height": 640,
        "width": 1184,
